collectors.titleDetails: (15 total Queries, 15 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT SUM(net_sales) as gross_order FROM (SELECT (amount - max(cost)) as net_sales FROM `reports` JOIN transactions ON reports.sku = transactions.sku WHERE client_id='493' AND `transaction-master-id` = '10' AND (reports.qty < 2 OR reports.qty IS NULL) GROUP BY `order-id`) as n

SELECT transactions.sku, repo FROM transactions LEFT JOIN (SELECT reports.sku as repo FROM reports WHERE client_id = '493') as r ON transactions.sku = r.repo WHERE `transaction-master-id` = '10' AND transactions.sku IS NOT NULL AND repo IS NULL GROUP BY transactions.sku
